==English==

===Etymology===
{{root|en|ine-pro|*(s)ker- (turn)}}
From {{inh|en|enm|schrynken}}, from {{inh|en|ang|sċrincan}}, from {{inh|en|gem-pro|*skrinkwaną}}. Cognate with {{cog|nl|schrinken||to shrink}}.

The sense {{m-g|psychologist, psychotherapist}} is a {{clipping|en|headshrinker|nocap=1}}.

